text: Mthokozisi Nkululeko Nxumalo (7 January 19891 August 2021) was a South African politician. He was a Member of the National Assembly from May 2019 until his death in August 2021. He was a member of the Inkatha Freedom Party. Nxumalo was born in Vryheid, South Africa. Nxumalo was killed in a car crash on 1 August 2021 in Nongoma, South Africa at the age of 32. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Road accident deaths Category:South African MPs
